      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9]{Theorem (Ex)}</p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can use a ranged injection weapon to quickly render emergency medical aid to a willing or unconscious creature within the first range increment of the weapon used. At 10th and 15th levels, this range increases by 10 feet (+[[lookupRange(@classes.biohacker.levels, 0, 10, 10, 15, 20)]]feet). The target regains a number of Stamina Points equal to your biohacker level + your key ability score modifier. A target can be affected by this ability only once per day.</p>"
